ass="headerlink" title="1.7.2 词例"></a>1.7.2 词例</h3><p>お名前わ？</p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001170105863.png" alt="image-20251001170105863"></p><h2 id="1-8-や行"><a href="#1-8-や行" class="headerlink" title="1.8 や行"></a>1.8 や行</h2><h3 id="1-8-1-写法"><a href="#1-8-1-写法" class="headerlink" title="1.8.1 写法"></a>1.8.1 写法</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001155623397.png" alt="image-20251001155623397"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001155732877.png" alt="image-20251001155732877"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001155802398.png" alt="image-20251001155802398"></p><h3 id="1-8-2-词例"><a href="#1-8-2-词例" class="headerlink" title="1.8.2 词例"></a>1.8.2 词例</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001170353197.png" alt="image-20251001170353197"></p><h2 id="1-9-ら行"><a href="#1-9-ら行" class="headerlink" title="1.9 ら行"></a>1.9 ら行</h2><h3 id="1-9-1-写法"><a href="#1-9-1-写法" class="headerlink" title="1.9.1 写法"></a>1.9.1 写法</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001155858314.png" alt="image-20251001155858314"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001155930166.png" alt="image-20251001155930166"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160019062.png" alt="image-20251001160019062"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160050827.png" alt="image-20251001160050827"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160105182.png" alt="image-20251001160105182"></p><h3 id="1-9-2-词例"><a href="#1-9-2-词例" class="headerlink" title="1.9.2 词例"></a>1.9.2 词例</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001172108341.png" alt="image-20251001172108341"></p><h2 id="1-10-わ行"><a href="#1-10-わ行" class="headerlink" title="1.10 わ行"></a>1.10 わ行</h2><h3 id="1-10-1-写法"><a href="#1-10-1-写法" class="headerlink" title="1.10.1 写法"></a>1.10.1 写法</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160232411.png" alt="image-20251001160232411"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160306111.png" alt="描述"><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160314303.png" alt="描述"></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001160401050.png" alt="image-20251001160401050"></p><h3 id="1-10-2-词例"><a href="#1-10-2-词例" class="headerlink" title="1.10.2 词例"></a>1.10.2 词例</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001172341927.png" alt="image-20251001172341927"></p><h2 id="1-11-外来语单词"><a href="#1-11-外来语单词" class="headerlink" title="1.11 外来语单词"></a>1.11 外来语单词</h2><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001172655904.png" alt="image-20251001172655904"></p><h1 id="2、日语的读音"><a href="#2、日语的读音" class="headerlink" title="2、日语的读音"></a>2、日语的读音</h1><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20250921165029192.png" alt="image-20250921165029192"></p><p>0型音：就是第一个假名正常读，第二个音就要往上读，剩下的假名的读法和第二个音一样</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/0%E5%9E%8B%E9%9F%B3.m4a" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>4型音：从第4个假名开始往下降，前面都是和0型音一样</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/4%E5%9E%8B%E9%9F%B3.m4a" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>5型音：</p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20250921205548364.png" alt="image-20250921205548364"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/5%E5%9E%8B%E9%9F%B3.m4a" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>3型音：从第3个假名开始往下降，前面都是和0型音一样</p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20250921205745035.png" alt="image-20250921205745035"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/3%E5%9E%8B%E9%9F%B3.m4a" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>2型音：从第2个假名开始往下降，前面都是和0型音一样</p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20250921210001646.png" alt="image-20250921210001646"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/2%E5%9E%8B%E9%9F%B3.m4a" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>1型音：从第1个假名开始往下降，<strong>然后把第一个音升上去</strong></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20250921210813753.png" alt="image-20250921210813753"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/%E5%BD%95%E9%9F%B3%20(4).m4a" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><h1 id="3、日语读音规则"><a href="#3、日语读音规则" class="headerlink" title="3、日语读音规则"></a>3、日语读音规则</h1><h2 id="3-1-拨音（ん）"><a href="#3-1-拨音（ん）" class="headerlink" title="3.1 拨音（ん）"></a>3.1 拨音（ん）</h2><p>日语音节末出现「ん」称为拨音。与汉语鼻音相类似。它的发音根据后面的音节有所变化。发音时占一个音拍。拨音（ん）会根据它后面所接的假名的不同，发不同的音：</p><ul><li>在た行、だ行、ら行、な行音节前面发/n/音；あん　ぃん…</li><li>在ば行、ぱ行、ま行音节前面发/m/；</li><li>在か行、が行及其他音节前面发/ng/ 。</li></ul><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251001174652253.png" alt="image-20251001174652253"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/102%23198949778%23f002.mp3" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198940881%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686613197448" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198933270%23f002.mp3?vTag=1736753416186" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198983079%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686560307479" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>あん（an）</p><p>いん（in）</p><p>うん (uh 听来有点像uen)</p><p>えん(eh注意e的读音后面有一个en的音)</p><p>おん(oh 读音类似ong，是一个连贯的读音)</p><p>かん(读音痛起来类似kan)</p><p>きん（kin）</p><p>くん（kun）</p><p>けん（类似英文的can）</p><p>こん（kong）</p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251002222245845.png" alt="image-20251002222245845"></p><h2 id="3-2-常用寒暄语"><a href="#3-2-常用寒暄语" class="headerlink" title="3.2 常用寒暄语"></a>3.2 常用寒暄语</h2><ul><li><p>初（はじ）めまして。 ④　初次见面<br><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251003011034692.png" alt="image-20251003011034692"></p></li><li><p>よろしくお願いします。 ⓪＋⑥　请多关照<br><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251003011314267.png" alt="image-20251003011314267"></p></li><li><p>こちらこそよろしくお願いします。　④</p></li><li><p>お久しぶりです。　⑦ 好久不见　<br>ふ(fu)　ぶ(bu)</p></li><li><p>また明日（あした）。：明天见　またね、また今度ね（またこんどね）</p></li><li><p>お疲れ様でした。　⑦ 您辛苦了（只用于平辈或者对下属使用）</p><p>回复的时候也可以直接使用这句话</p></li></ul><h2 id="3-3-浊音、半浊音的读音"><a href="#3-3-浊音、半浊音的读音" class="headerlink" title="3.3 浊音、半浊音的读音"></a>3.3 浊音、半浊音的读音</h2><h3 id="3-3-1-浊音"><a href="#3-3-1-浊音" class="headerlink" title="3.3.1 浊音"></a>3.3.1 浊音</h3><p>浊音就是在假名的右上角加上两个小点，但是并不所有的假名都可以有浊音的ka行中<code>k</code>是可以被浊化的，读作<code>g</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>假名</th><th>罗马字</th><th>浊化</th><th>罗马字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>か/カ</td><td>ka</td><td>が/ガ</td><td>ga</td></tr><tr><td>き/キ</td><td>ki</td><td>ぎ/ギ</td><td>gi</td></tr><tr><td>く/ク</td><td>ku</td><td>ぐ/グ</td><td>gu</td></tr><tr><td>け/ケ</td><td>ke</td><td>げ/ゲ</td><td>ge</td></tr><tr><td>こ/コ</td><td>ko</td><td>ご/ ゴ</td><td>go</td></tr></tbody></table><p>sa行也是有浊音的，其中的<code>s</code>会被浊化成<code>z</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>假名</th><th>罗马字</th><th>浊化</th><th>罗马字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>さ/サ</td><td>sa</td><td>ざ/ザ</td><td>za</td></tr><tr><td>し/シ</td><td>shi</td><td>じ/ジ</td><td>ji</td></tr><tr><td>す/ス</td><td>su</td><td>ず/ズ</td><td>zu</td></tr><tr><td>せ/セ</td><td>se</td><td>ぜ/ゼ</td><td>ze</td></tr><tr><td>そ/ソ</td><td>so</td><td>ぞ/ゾ</td><td>zo</td></tr></tbody></table><p>ta行也有浊音，其中的<code>t</code>会被浊化成<code>d</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>假名</th><th>罗马字</th><th>浊化</th><th>罗马字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>た/タ</td><td>ta</td><td>だ/ダ</td><td>da</td></tr><tr><td>ち/チ</td><td>chi</td><td>ぢ/ヂ</td><td>读作di，<br>(不常用)读法上和 上面的じ一致</td></tr><tr><td>つ/ツ</td><td>tsu</td><td>づ/ヅ</td><td>读作du<br><br>(不常用)读法上和上面的ず一致</td></tr><tr><td>て/ テ</td><td>te</td><td>で/デ</td><td>de</td></tr><tr><td>と/ト</td><td>to</td><td>ど/ド</td><td>do</td></tr></tbody></table><p>ha行也有浊音，其中的<code>h</code>会被浊化成<code>b</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>假名</th><th>罗马字</th><th>浊化</th><th>罗马字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>は/ハ</td><td>ha</td><td>ば/バ</td><td>ba</td></tr><tr><td>ひ/ヒ</td><td>hi</td><td>び/ビ</td><td>bi</td></tr><tr><td>ふ/フ</td><td>fu</td><td>ぶ/ブ</td><td>bu</td></tr><tr><td>へ/ヘ</td><td>he</td><td>べ/ベ</td><td>be</td></tr><tr><td>ほ/ホ</td><td>ho</td><td>ぼ/ボ</td><td>bo</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="3-3-2-半浊音"><a href="#3-3-2-半浊音" class="headerlink" title="3.3.2 半浊音"></a>3.3.2 半浊音</h3><p>半浊音只有一行，就是ha行，其中的<code>h</code>会被半浊化成<code>p</code>，写法上就是在假名右上方加上小圈</p><table><thead><tr><th>假名</th><th>罗马字</th><th>半浊化</th><th>罗马字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>は/ハ</td><td>ha</td><td>ぱ/パ</td><td>pa</td></tr><tr><td>ひ/ヒ</td><td>hi</td><td>ぴ/ピ</td><td>pi</td></tr><tr><td>ふ/フ</td><td>fu</td><td>ぷ/プ</td><td>pu</td></tr><tr><td>へ/ヘ</td><td>he</td><td>ぺ/ペ</td><td>pe</td></tr><tr><td>ほ/ホ</td><td>ho</td><td>ぽ/ポ</td><td>po</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="3-3-3-浊音的单词发音"><a href="#3-3-3-浊音的单词发音" class="headerlink" title="3.3.3 浊音的单词发音"></a>3.3.3 浊音的单词发音</h3><p><strong>が行</strong></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251005080157318.png" alt="image-20251005080157318"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198952051%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686580649939" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198943249%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686643300290" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198943844%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686612346266" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198950319%23f002.mp3?vTag=1746752659754" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198993603%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686577312356" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>日本人、日本、日本语的发音都有些微妙的不同，放在一起以示区别</p><p>日本人④（にほんじん）：</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198993611%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686550327879" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>日本②（にほん）：</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198993588%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686630439758" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>日本語⓪（にほんご）</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198993603%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686577312356" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p><strong>ざ行</strong></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251005082854531.png" alt="image-20251005082854531"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198943293%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686877398747" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198971747%23f002.mp3?vTag=1709605566660" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198913215%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686562065347" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198978531%23f002.mp3?vTag=1723197321292" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198936431%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686563022651" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p><strong>だ行</strong></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251005083103257.png" alt="image-20251005083103257"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%234z4CmgFW7O%23f002.mp3?vTag=1689077793960" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198965921%23f002.mp3?vTag=1687336984425" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198980780%23f002.mp3?vTag=1687338136065" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198989380%23f002.mp3?vTag=1708240594149" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23jWnVXOOc8o%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686632857001" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p><strong>ば行</strong></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="/%E6%A2%81%E7%88%BD%E6%97%A5%E8%AF%AD.assets/image-20251005084414854.png" alt="image-20251005084414854"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%2319899930%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686585149438" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198922118%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686616314993" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%231989101586%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686572907210" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23220120w208244%23f002.mp3?vTag=1753603391777" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23CBPqS2wYov%23f002.mp3?vTag=1710009200353" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p><strong>半浊音</strong></p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251005085337121.png" alt="image-20251005085337121"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198921494%23f002.mp3?vTag=1732260205413" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198922327%23f002.mp3?vTag=1706092752062" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198923983%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686638302442" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23iEOvQnZN75%23f002.mp3?vTag=1709812535955" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198972420%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686567778223" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><h2 id="3-4-拗音的读音"><a href="#3-4-拗音的读音" class="headerlink" title="3.4 拗音的读音"></a>3.4 拗音的读音</h2><p>经常能看到有的假名大有的假名小，像这种一大一小的组合就叫做拗音，一大一小组合在一起读一拍</p><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251005161601059.png" alt="image-20251005161601059"></p><p>在五十音表中黄色的就是拗音中的大的假名，小的就是绿色部分</p><table><thead><tr><th>平假名</th><th>や</th><th>ゆ</th><th>よ</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>き</td><td>きゃ（kya）</td><td>きゅ(kyu)</td><td>きょ(kyo)</td></tr><tr><td>し</td><td>しゃ (sha，sya)</td><td>しゅ (shu，syu)</td><td>しょ (sho，syo)</td></tr><tr><td>ち</td><td>ちゃ(cha)</td><td>ちゅ (chu)</td><td>ちょ (cho)</td></tr><tr><td>に</td><td>にゃ (nya)</td><td>にゅ (nyu)</td><td>にょ (nyo)</td></tr><tr><td>ひ</td><td>ひゃ (hya)</td><td>ひゅ (hyu)</td><td>ひょ (hyo)</td></tr><tr><td>み</td><td>みゃ (mya)</td><td>みゅ (myu)</td><td>みょ (myo)</td></tr><tr><td>り</td><td>りゃ (rya)</td><td>りゅ (ryu)</td><td>りょ (ryo)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>ぎ</strong></td><td>ぎゃ (gya)</td><td>ぎゅ (gyu)</td><td>ぎょ (gyo)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>じ</strong>/<strong>ぢ(ji)</strong></td><td>じゃ/ぢゃ (ja),ぢゃ不存在</td><td>じゅ/ぢゅ (ju) ，ぢゅ不存在</td><td>じょ/ぢょ (jo)， ぢょ不存在</td></tr><tr><td><strong>び</strong><strong>(bi)</strong></td><td>びゃ (bya)</td><td>びゅ (byu)</td><td>びょ (byo)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>ぴ(pi)</strong></td><td>ぴゃ (pya)</td><td>ぴゅ (pyu)</td><td>ぴょ (pyo)</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251005164547664.png" alt="image-20251005164547664"></p><h3 id="3-4-1-常用的拗音词例认读"><a href="#3-4-1-常用的拗音词例认读" class="headerlink" title="3.4.1 常用的拗音词例认读"></a>3.4.1 常用的拗音词例认读</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251006174514376.png" alt="image-20251006174514376"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%231989802%23f002.mp3?vTag=1709543787489" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198910116%23f002.mp3?vTag=1754906174710" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198965837%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686613940205" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198944384%23f002.mp3?vTag=1720400663838" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198962456%23f002.mp3?vTag=1713512580041" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198971879%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686573373643" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198936625%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686632191313" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198985986%23f002.mp3?vTag=1710926816733" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251006180501038.png" alt="image-20251006180501038"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198926008%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686626413291" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>manyuaru</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%231989105864%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686586612549" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198998766%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686583509889" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198958001%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686637346943" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198972915%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686617452414" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%231989111519%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686632572973" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198922421%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686716930233" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><h3 id="3-4-2-外来语拗音"><a href="#3-4-2-外来语拗音" class="headerlink" title="3.4.2 外来语拗音"></a>3.4.2 外来语拗音</h3><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251006211643138.png" alt="image-20251006211643138"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%236EAuYVQ5lq%23f002.mp3?vTag=1736402516774" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%2319895751%23f002.mp3?vTag=1711434824661" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>aidia</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%2319897936%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686710783191" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>webusaito</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198913902%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686709440982" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198922714%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686619267863" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198925227%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686623746777" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>borantia</p><h2 id="3-5-常用的寒暄语"><a href="#3-5-常用的寒暄语" class="headerlink" title="3.5 常用的寒暄语"></a>3.5 常用的寒暄语</h2><h3 id="3-5-1-回家时的寒暄语"><a href="#3-5-1-回家时的寒暄语" class="headerlink" title="3.5.1 回家时的寒暄语"></a>3.5.1 回家时的寒暄语</h3><ul><li>ただいま　④　我回来了</li><li>お帰りなさい　⑥    或者和家人可以说：お帰り    欢迎回家</li></ul><h3 id="3-5-2-问候的寒暄语"><a href="#3-5-2-问候的寒暄语" class="headerlink" title="3.5.2 问候的寒暄语"></a>3.5.2 问候的寒暄语</h3><ul><li><p>お元（げん）気（き）ですか　②  元気表示身体健康有活力，您身体好吗？</p><blockquote><p>日语当中不太使用主语，可以使用お代表比较礼貌的您从而代替主语；最后的か表示这是一个疑问句，读法上语气稍微上扬，注意か不要读成ga，而是ka</p></blockquote></li><li><p>おかげさまで     元気です　⓪＋①</p><blockquote><p>おかげさまで：表示托您的福，这是一个很有礼貌的回复，这句话完整意思是：托您的福我身体很好</p></blockquote></li></ul><h2 id="3-6-促音（つ）"><a href="#3-6-促音（つ）" class="headerlink" title="3.6 促音（つ）"></a>3.6 促音（つ）</h2><p>つ这个假名有时候也会写的小一点，这个时候在单词的读音当中要空一拍（停一下）</p><blockquote><p>注意促音っ的打法就是看后面的假名，比如しょっき，っ的后面是きki，那么就双写k然后加i</p><p>shokki</p></blockquote><p><img src="/medias/loading.gif" data-original="https://tonyxue.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/note_img/image-20251006220459271.png" alt="image-20251006220459271"></p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%231989113616%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686715128561" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>roppyaku</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%231989106872%23f002.mp3?vTag=1687338035338" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>asatte</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198943371%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686569629479" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>kissaten</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198957661%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686586459977" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>zasshi</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198928188%23f002.mp3?vTag=1723516146617" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>rippa</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%2319895370%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686568167485" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>yukkuri</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198917517%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686573076984" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>chotto</p><audio controls=""><source src="https://oss.mojidict.com/tts_v2/102%23198970427%23f002.mp3?vTag=1686581390369" type="audio/mpeg"></audio><p>shokki</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
